list.abstract: wake，英文单词，动词、名词，作及物动词译为“唤醒；唤起；为……守灵”，作不及物动词译为“醒来；唤醒；警觉”；作名词译为“守夜；航迹”。

这是导演Henry LeRoy Finch首次编剧和执导的作品，他的妻子Susan Landau是制片人，Susan的爸爸马丁·兰道(曾获奥斯卡奖)在片中客串出演了老年Sebastian一角。电影在美国东北部缅因州一家1745年建立的老房子里拍摄的。这部片子是夫妻俩低成本独立电影制作的实验品，全片用数码照相机拍摄，后期制作是在电脑上加入电影效果完成。影片讲叙四兄弟之间纠葛的恩怨情仇。导演对家庭的题材似乎很感兴趣，这是他撰写家庭三部曲中的一部，也是他第一部执拍的作品。

yingyinNormal.en: Please wake up, Hatter. Please. Wake up. Please wake up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 醒一醒，疯帽子，求你。醒来吧，求你醒醒吧。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《爱丽丝梦游仙境2：镜中奇遇记》

yingyinNormal.en: And then wake up in the morning and do it some more.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然后早上醒来又继续。

yingyinNormal.en: So I wake up in my younger body, God knows where, then what?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我会在我年轻时的身体中醒来，鬼知那是哪，接着呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Then you can have a good night's rest and wake up tomorrow fresh on Abu Dhabi time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 之后您可以安睡一整晚，明天醒来神清气爽。

yingyinNormal.en: At least you get to wake up from your nightmare. I'm living with mine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你起码可以从噩梦中醒来，我现在得一直生活在噩梦中。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and George have fallen to sleep. When they wake up, it will be Christmas day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇和乔治已经睡着了。等他们醒来就到圣诞节了。

yingyinNormal.en: Dreams make good stories, but everything important happens when we're wake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 梦境会编织骗人的幻象，可重要的事情都发生在醒来之后。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, gorgeous, you're back to the races. You're gonna wake in three, two, one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，美人你可以回归赛场了，三、二、一 、醒来。

yingyinNormal.en: We can't do that, that's insane. I mean A: he could wake up and B: You know let's go for it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不行，你疯了，第一，他可能醒来 第二，管他的。

yingyinNormal.en: But once you wake up, whatever you've done will take hold and become history.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是，只要你一旦醒来，你所做的任何事都会固定下来，变成历史。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll do it. Sheldon, wait. You have to wake up first. Oh, of course. Set phasers to dumb, right?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我会这么做。谢尔顿，等等，你得先醒来。当然，先设好相位仪，对吧。

yingyinNormal.en: That's right, Dolores. You're in a dream. Would you like to wake up from this dream? Yes. I'm terrified.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错，德洛丽丝，你在梦里，你想从梦里醒来吗？是的，我很害怕。

yingyinNormal.en: The bullet grazed his cortical shield. It's not pretty, but he should be functional. Wake up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 子弹擦过了他脑皮层表面，虽然挺严重，但是他应该还是可以运作的。醒来。

yingyinNormal.en: But then I would wake up and the voice would start all over again. So I ran away. Crossed the shining sea.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但接着我会醒来，这个声音再度响起，所以我逃跑了，越过大洋到达彼岸。

yingyinNormal.en: When I went under, the world was at war. I wake up. They say we won. They didn't say what we lost.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我昏过去的时候，这个世界在打仗。醒来以后听说我们赢了，不知道赢的代价是什么。

yingyinNormal.en: She's cold as ice. Ginny, please don't be dead. Wake up. You've got to help me, Tom. There's a basilisk.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她就跟冰块一样冷。金妮，求求你别死。快醒来。你必须帮帮我，汤姆。这里头有蛇怪。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: I'd be trapped inside a huge egg and this monster would open his jaws and start to devour me. I'd wake up just in time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 梦见自己被困在巨型鸡蛋里，怪物张嘴将我吞入囊中，所幸每次都能及时醒来。

yingyinNormal.en: When I wake. What? That's the name of the song. Jackie Hill, July 17th, 1938, Bob Ellis on the drums.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当我醒来。什么？这首歌的名字，杰基·希尔，1938年7月17，鼓手是鲍勃·埃里森。

yingyinNormal.en: Good night, Peppa. Good night, George. Peppa and George have fallen to sleep. When they wake up, it will be Christmas day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 晚安了佩奇，晚安了，乔治。佩奇和乔治已经睡着了。等他们醒来就到圣诞节了。

yingyinNormal.en: If you wake up one morning with 1,000 times the strength you had the night before, how will you handle delicate day-to-day tasks?
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果某天早上你醒来发现你的力量是昨晚的一千倍，你该如何处理那些日常的精细活？

word_usage.usage:
wake up作“把某人叫醒”时up是副词，用作其宾语的代词通常需放在中间。
示例：我妈妈经常很早就把我叫醒。
误 My mother often wakes up me in the early morning.
正 My mother often wakes me up in the early morning.

wake up作“醒来”时表示瞬间动作，不能和表示“一段时间”的时间状语连用。
示例：他已经醒了很长时间了。
误 He has waken up for some time.
正 He has been awake for some time.
wake和awake都有“唤醒，醒来”的意思。wake是最常用词，awake则比wake正式些。如指“醒来，使醒来”，最好用wake。
